{"tid":2289333,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"8.31暴動案 前高級督察作供 承認記錯案發地點","createTime":"2020-11-17T07:46:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-17T15:18:38.000Z","uid":240362,"like":9,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"814f22b90c4e78c5214d0763ecdd8bcbb0308d27","tid":2289333,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T07:46:33.000Z","msg":"去年8月31日港島區遊行演變成衝突，多人在銅鑼灣和灣仔被捕，15名人被控罪動，涉及其中7名被告的案件今在區域法院續審。因個人原因離開警隊、當日的小隊女指揮官今供稱，當日警方在崇光百貨外設立防線，她留意到早前曾有汽油彈從示威人群中「郁緊嘅人頭」後方掟出，並觀察有一小撮人行來行去，疑似「正組織計劃一啲嘢」，情況令人擔憂，故指揮小隊成員推進拘捕。惟辯方盤問時，她改口稱當日多次遇到類似情況，「令人擔憂」的情況有機會是較早時在其他街口發生。<br />\n<br />\n講錯街名 解釋：之前冇守過銅鑼灣<br />\n<br />\n盤問下，她翻看地圖後澄清，當時集合隊員的位置並非「怡和街」，而是記利佐治街，並解釋「之前冇守過銅鑼灣」。梁看過片段後再澄清，其實自己當時在警方防線中後排，看不到自己的小隊，片中亦聽不到自己的警告。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201117/GUBW5JZZHFA3XPR55HGTQ4SIVE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201117%2FGUBW5JZZHFA3XPR55HGTQ4SIVE%2F&d=gkHqMR5YDMJAUJmZ80XM4x%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=b297dc78\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201117%2FGUBW5JZZHFA3XPR55HGTQ4SIVE%2F&h=0c0d3e08\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201117/GUBW5JZZHFA3XPR55HGTQ4SIVE/</a>"},{"pid":"b815a50289a9a66a9f2d99a1094bff8a56f85ea0","tid":2289333,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T07:49:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52398cd1c55a2ac4c0a3e9df77989c15c0e55a19","tid":2289333,"uid":127929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T07:50:31.000Z","msg":"死全家"},{"pid":"e9cae8caaa27dbac75200e26ff349154776b75b4","tid":2289333,"uid":139203,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"52